        "content": "Testing ensures your game functions as intended. \n- Identify bugs early. \n- Improve game quality."
      },
      {
        "title": "Common Debugging Techniques",
        "content": "Utilize various methods to find and fix issues. \n- Print statements for tracking. \n- Use debugging tools. \n- Check error messages."
